.SH SYNOPSIS
.sp
\fBpci_device [\-h] [\-E] device\-filter [{aer,remove,rescan,topology,unbind,vf}]\fP
.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
pci_device is a tool to aid in common operations for managing PCIe devices and
drivers.
.SH OPTIONS
